{"tid":1598599,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣現身！Switch《健身環大冒險》廣告片釋出","createTime":"2019-09-27T14:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T05:02:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9973011e788282105121f0a9972600d159a6de7e","tid":1598599,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:19:41.000Z","msg":"國民老婆現身！任天堂最新的健身冒險遊戲《健身環大冒險》已經進入市場宣傳的階段，這次請來新垣結衣出演電視廣告片，整體保持著任天堂的風格，而新垣結衣的可愛當然起到了畫龍點睛之效。<br />\n <br />\n《健身環大冒險》中擁有超過 40 種健身招式，分別為紅色（鍛鍊手部）、黃色（鍛鍊核心肌群）、藍色（鍛鍊腿部）、綠色（瑜珈）等 4 類，概念就像運動結尾要收操，玩家需按照敵人的顏色來做出對應的招數，除了解任務的模式，還可以選擇「快速玩」模式，讓玩家單純的選擇要進行的健身動作，進行簡單的小遊戲。<br />\n <br />\n「Ring-Con」與「腿部固定帶」需搭配 Nintendo Switch 主機，並分別將 Joy-Con 控制器，安裝在配件上，才可以感應玩家的行為和動作。"},{"pid":"beb025795bba1cb7eff2b5109b658e02a5a32822","tid":1598599,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auVPgPR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauVPgPR.jpg&h=1e259d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PeUgGgy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPeUgGgy.jpg&h=4b25c2a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2d4da5814651f769f8c518773535397adeb0c50","tid":1598599,"uid":149496,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100fd4fa5d333855014a63a87de41e2e68d6fa43","tid":1598599,"uid":54579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e2d4da5814651f769f8c518773535397adeb0c50","tid":1598599,"uid":149496,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"伯母老d"},{"pid":"41c5796cf5f3ce187391725771f6712fe34ea464","tid":1598599,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:26:11.